* Carnage smiled, just try it! She then growled and took a step towards the 
clone, she had no fear because she knew that she could fight back."

" I've been online for only a few days but I've been on this planet before, 
I used to fight alongside Megatron until he killed my best friend. Now I 
hate his guts and wouldn't think of anything sweeter then seeing his mech 
fluid on my blade and his dead body at my feet!
And the next time you attack somebot make sure they are who you think they 
are!"

* Carnage bared her teeth.*

" And the next time make sure that you don't get attacked yourself! You 
idiot! If I hadn't got that creature in the eye then you would be sitting in 
the pit of it's stomach right now, so watch it!
And further more, don't threaten me unless you can back your claim!"

* Carnage snarled and clenched her fist, if this clone was going to attack 
her then she was ready and willing!*
